{
  "bookId": "laozi-heshanggong-wiki",
  "num": 10,
  "title": "第十章（能為）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "載營魄，"
    },
    {
      "text": "抱一，能無離乎，"
    },
    {
      "text": "專氣致柔，"
    },
    {
      "text": "能嬰兒。"
    },
    {
      "text": "滌除玄覽，"
    },
    {
      "text": "能無疵。"
    },
    {
      "text": "愛民治國，"
    },
    {
      "text": "能無為。"
    },
    {
      "text": "天門開闔，"
    },
    {
      "text": "能為雌。"
    },
    {
      "text": "明白四達，"
    },
    {
      "text": "能無知。"
    },
    {
      "text": "生之、畜之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "生而不有，"
    },
    {
      "text": "為而不恃，"
    },
    {
      "text": "長而不宰，"
    },
    {
      "text": "是謂玄德。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "營魄，魂魄也。人載魂魄之上得以生，當愛養之。喜怒亡魂，卒驚傷魄。魂在肝，魄在肺。美酒甘肴，腐人肝肺。故魂靜志道不亂，魄安得壽延年也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言人能抱一，使不離於身，則長存。一者，道始所生，太和之精氣也。故曰：一布名於天下，天得一以清，地得一以寧，侯王得一以為正平，入為心，出為行，布施為德，摠名為一。一之為言，志一無二也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "專守精氣使不亂，則形體能應之而柔順。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "能如嬰兒內無思慮，外無政事，則精神不去也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "當洗其心，使潔淨也。心居玄冥之處，覽知萬事，故謂之玄覽也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不淫邪也，淨能無疵病乎。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "治身者，愛氣則身全；治國者，愛民則國安。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "治身者呼吸精氣，無令耳聞﹔治國者，布施惠德，無令下知也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天門謂北極紫微宮。開闔謂終始五際也。治身之天門謂鼻孔，開謂喘息也，闔謂呼吸也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "治身當如雌牝，安靜柔弱，治國應變，合而不唱也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言達明白，如日月四通，滿於天下八極之外。故曰：視之不見，聽之不聞，彰布之於十方，煥煥煌煌也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 4
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "無有能知道滿於天下者。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道生萬物而畜養之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 13,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道生萬物，無所取有。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 14,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道所施為，不恃望其報也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-16",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 15,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道長養萬物，不宰割以為器用。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-17",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 16,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言道行德，玄冥不可得見，欲使人如道也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
